**Performance Tiers**:
- ⚡ Cheapest: `opacity`, `transform`, `filter`
- ⚠️ Moderate: color, background-color
- 🐌 Expensive: width, height, padding, margin, border
- 🔥 Very Expensive: properties triggering reflow on complex layouts

